{"title":"瑶家心向太阳城","authors":["潘爱莲"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":11,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"瑶家心向太阳城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广西都安瑶族自治县琴棋公社家帮生产队共青团支部委员  潘爱莲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百鸟欢歌唱不停，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红花露脸笑盈盈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青山绿水齐舞动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢送瑶女上北京。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娘送女儿上山坳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千句嘱言要记牢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见了主席问声好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谢他为咱把心操。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹送我上了船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥手欢歌喜连连；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千言万语难说尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一人吃瓜万人甜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记送我出寨前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘱咐鼓励千万遍；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会议精神学习好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满载而归返家园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大爷送我红河边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热泪盈眶把话言；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫我莫忘阶级恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心跟党永向前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮红日东边升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瑶女心向太阳城；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带上瑶家一片心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插翅飞往北京城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1964．11．21于北京"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}